<div class="user-guide-page container">
  <h1><%= page.title %></h1>
  <p class="lead"><%= page.description %></p>

  <div class="guide-screenshot mb-4">
    <img src="<%= page.screenshotUrl %>" alt="<%= page.title %> screenshot" class="img-fluid border" />
  </div>

  <h2>Sponsor details and visibility</h2>
  <p>The Sponsor Details page shows the sponsor profile, logo, description and whether they are publicly visible on the site.</p>

  <h3>Fields explained</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Name</strong> — sponsor's public name.</li>
    <li><strong>Website</strong> — link to the sponsor's site.</li>
    <li><strong>Description</strong> — short information about the sponsor and relationship with the club.</li>
    <li><strong>Publicly visible</strong> — toggle to control whether this sponsor appears in the public sponsor directory.</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Editing a sponsor</h3>
  <ol>
    <li>Click <em>Edit</em> to update sponsor information.</li>
    <li>Upload a new logo if needed.</li>
    <li>Save changes to update the sponsor profile.</li>
  </ol>

  <p class="mt-3"><a href="<%= page.url.replace(':id', '51') %>">Open an example sponsor page</a></p>
  <p><a href="/user-guide">Back to guide index</a></p>
</div>
